description:
This is a 52 minute workout called '50 MIN FULL BODY WORKOUT || At-Home Pilates' from the channel Move With Nicole.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging and Moderate.

Original workout description: Free up some time for yourself and enjoy this 50 Minute Full Body Pilates class! This full body workout will not only work your entire body but will leave you feeling strong, energised and more centred! All you need is yourself and a mat, no equipment needed. Have fun! :)

♡ INSTAGRAM: @movewithnicole


♫ Music from https://www.epidemicsound.com/
